creator: Ella Wheeler Wilcox
description:
LibriVox recording of Poems of Power by Ella Wheeler Wilcox.
Read in English by Julia Niedermaier; Crln Yldz Ksr; Kristin Gjerløw; Ken Masters; Travis Wakeman; Shakira Searle; bean420; Richard Carter; Joseph Tabler; AnnaMarie Tokas; Greg Giordano; Rani K.; Ian King; Rosslyn Carlyle; Freya Hansen; Carol Box; Ian Quinlan; sgvine; DomBombadil; keetah2015; David Lawrence
This is a volume in a series of books of poetry by Ella Wheeler Wilcox. This time, the theme is "Power". - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
